id: monica-typescript7-spike
title: Re-evaluate TypeScript 7 ecosystem compatibility
description: Check whether TypeScript-ESLint and the CLI toolchain support TypeScript 7 without peer-range violations or behavior regressions.
type: Spike
status: open
priority: 2
