acceptance_criteria: Peer ranges permit TypeScript 7; typecheck/lint/build/tests pass in an isolated branch; migration notes and decision are recorded
definition_of_ready: @typescript-eslint publishes a release whose TypeScript peer range includes 7.x.
goal: trusted-monica-cli
objective: current-compatible-typescript
value: Avoid indefinite toolchain drift
impact: Keeps type tooling current without forcing unsupported combinations
outcome: Evidence-backed adopt-or-defer decision
why_now: TypeScript 7 is registry-latest but incompatible with the current linter peer contract
