comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:08:56.033Z",codex-root,Created from the July 2026 modernization decision; not required to close the critical advisory.
  "2026-07-16T17:19:06.369Z",codex-root,"Dependabot PR #48 confirmed the current incompatibility on 2026-07-16: TypeScript 7.0.2 failed both Validate (Bun) and Validate (Node + npm/npx). PR closed and >=7 updates ignored until the definition-of-ready peer range is satisfied."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:08:56.033Z",codex-root,Start by querying @typescript-eslint parser and plugin peerDependencies.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:08:56.033Z",codex-root,Registry latest and ecosystem-compatible latest can differ across coupled compiler/linter releases.
files[1]{path,scope,note}:
  package.json,project,compiler and linter versions
tests[1]{command,scope,note}:
  bun run typecheck,project,compiler migration gate
docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
